Package: fml
Version: 1.1.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Kevin Melangert <kosikevinonu@gmail.com>
Installed-Size: 28
Depends: bash (>= 4.0), procps.
Recommends: sudo
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/Melangert/Fix-My-Laptop-FML-
Description: Lightweight Linux maintenance tool for low-spec systems
 fml (Fix My Linux) is designed for older and low-resource Linux machines.
 It has zero dependencies beyond bash and uses no background processes.
 .
 Supports APT, DNF, Pacman, Zypper, Flatpak, and Snap cleanup.
